In this section we are going to look at
control flow => controlling the order of
what gets executed in our program.

We'll address:
    => Comparison Operators
    => Logical Operators
        +How to use them to implement rules/logic
    => Conditional Statements
        +How to use them to make decisions in our program
    => Loops
        +How to use them to execute code repetitively
    => Error Handling
